description
From: http://myeigenharp.wordpress.com/2013/3/27/octave-talker/
Octave talker, the switching logic to set the global variable:
  variable octave step
used in MH004

Phrase: 'octave talker hey re do' forces recompile of Belcanto in the talker

script
empty join
green talker listen
1 called 1 cancel
2 called 1 cancel

"
empty join
1 as octave step define
octave talker hey re do
" when 1 called 1 do

"
empty join
0.33333333333333331 as octave step define
octave talker hey re do
" when 2 called 1 do
